           SHORT="psutils provides utilities for manipulating PostScript files."
cat << EOF

A small set of invaluable utilities for manipulating PostScript files by
selecting certain pages, re-ordering pages to facilitate printing books,
changing the paper size, fitting several pages on a single sheet, etc.  This
package also includes some utilities to "fix" some broken PostScript formats.

EOF
